{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-10244/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-10244"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:02:44"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["close-up"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["single shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man looks up at a woman."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10244/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-10244","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10244/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-10244"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10244/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10244/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10244/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10244/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10244/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10244/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10244/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10244/canvas/1/f29f89ae-570b-4e08-a551-996a7c81b864","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T17:49:36.749Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>By standing at the top of the stairs, Alma forces Reynolds to look upward, almost from a subservient position. Nevertheless, unlike Alma, he is shot in close-up with his face dominating the frame. He thus continues to retain control and power.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10244/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:404.53698394495257,312.6175458715596,295.1333142201835,311.96244266055044"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10244/canvas/1/b5e69609-e952-4164-aa06-f938d14404e6","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T17:50:11.897Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>As Reynolds looks up at Alma, light shines directly on his face, almost as if coming from Alma herself. She is trying to bring light into their relationship in this scene—planning a dinner in hopes of changing their routine and bringing them closer. However, Reynolds is resistant, uninterested in this change. This is not a light he welcomes.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10244/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:784.2603211009159,315.4415137614679,305.9991399082571,304.73767201834875"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10244/canvas/1/ed08ba97-e2a3-445d-9800-1cd619d744f4","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T17:50:30.066Z","creator":"Tallulah Stallvik","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The silhouette and cut of the dress resembles <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW20781036 BCX0\" href=\"https://digbmc.github.io/pt-annotated/items/phan-03557.html\"><u>the one she was fitted for</u></a> early in the film, the fabric of which she disliked. Here, she redoes it in her own style, simultaneously trying to fit in with his sensibilities and change them to accommodate her own. With this dinner, Alma is attempting to find a commonality between them, to meet him in the middle, while Reynolds resists any change or compromise.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-10244/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:26.275802752292137,24.493979357798032,252.92431192660558,228.7270642201835"}}}]}]}]}